Welcome!!!! To
See how to Hack

Requirements

• Members are to choose a code name
 
• Open a github account with your code name

• Start A game on overthesight

• Each member will be given an assignment to send here

• Don’t download anything from the Darkweb ....

• Your weekly Tasks will be pinned here ,you must finish it

Send your code name here to get registered

Let’s start hacking guys .....Good lüçk


You are all starting as a beginner

Your exploits per week gets you promoted here ....

.
Now we start :
I’m of the mindset you’ve watched the video , set up your github account, and have your Kali and termux already installed .
This is a practical class I’ll expect full cooperation otherwise this might lead to removal of any guilty individual.

There is a reason I asked you to check out the ssh  video earlier . Tho this does not show how you’d connect and co .
But you at least how to understand how it works .

See I can’t teach you everything, you’ll meet foreign configured networks , see new systems.
Your hacking basic knowledge must see you through .

I might teach you how to hack a laptop 👩‍💻 wirelessly.... you can use the same concept you learn to hack a car 🚗 ...


Just understand.... most 'script bies' out there don’t . They get softwares already built , they install it (even if it might be virus ) without understanding how it works ... and check how to use it online then bam....

 

You are an hacker for Gods sake not an app user .....


 pls kindly hack with ethics tho

INTRODUCTION TO WEB DEVELOPMENT 

 

 

Hey guys ....

 

I am 𝙊𝙡𝙖 I’m an engineering student.

I kinda into lots of programming languages, love learning them for fun .

 

Sometimes i get questions like :

Pls bro , what programming language should I learn first .

It's hard I know right?

But I’ll try as much as possible to drop my view on this :

You see ...

It depends on what you going into....

As as a Pentester  ? I'll advice you learn alllllll the programming languages, if you can , you don’t have to be the best in the any tho.

You don’t want to come across a system you can’t hack, just because you don’t understand the language. Also scripting language is important (Perl, python ....) . Programming languages like C, Assembly is also highly recommended 

 

As a Web Developer  ?

 

You choose ? Which of the languages you flow with.... I program my websites with python, A friend of mine does his with php

We do stuffs in same time frame

But it’s a like Must , a must to learn JavaScript or Typescript 

 

As an A.I specialist or Data Scientist?

 

I’ll ask you to go with python first , R too , then JavaScript s good too

 

 

As an engineer?

 

Programming languages like C and python , c++ are recommended

INTRODUCTION TO FOREX TRADING 

 

 

             COURSE UNAVAILABLE AT THE MOMENT

Full Beginners course on forex trading 

 

INTRODUCTION WHAT IS FOREX 
WHAT IS TRADED ON FOREX
WHO IS A FOREX BROOKER
TRADING TIMES & TRADING SESSIONS
TERMINOLOGIES USED IN FOREX.
FORMS OF TRADING
CURRENCY PAIRS.MT4 INTERFACE PART 1


What is a pip 
Lotsize concept of bid and ask price 
Trading orders forms of trading orders etc .
TRADING PLAN
MT4 INTERFACE PART 2


HOW TO KNOW WHEN TO ACTUALLY BUY OR SELL

HOW TO GENERATE SIGNALS FOR YOUR SELVES.

INDICATORS...Moving Averages, Stochastic, MACD, Bollinger bands, RSI, ADX, Parabolic SAR, ATR, Ichimoku.... etc


CHART ANALYSIS ETC.

Forex mastery class 

Full chart analysis 

Chart patterns  etc 

How to take partial profit  etc 

Trading with Price action 

 

And many more ......

WELCOME TO ETHICAL HACKING 101

COMMAND-LINE INTERFACE(CLI)

CLI is a command line program that accepts text input to execute operating system functions. unlike GUI(which uses pictures for interfacing)

CLI accepts texts and in turn converts it into executing a system function . Take for instance you were to shut down your laptop . normally a computer user would prefer GUI

 

A written text in your terminal can do this also , with a command 'shutdown now' on linux your computer can shutdown immediately

 

 

WHY COMMAND_LINE INTERFACE?

i know right .... why use the CLI when you can use GUI ? ...  not everyone likes typing to execute just a simple click if it were GUI. but CMD has its benefits . really it does ..

The original reason we use CLI is because of the greater control it gives . you will be very surprised to know the limits you have been trending as a GUI user.There are commands accessible only via shell that can control very complex operations on Unix/Linux and Windows machines.

Also, Pictures takes more memory hence more processor to use , tasks like bruteforcing which requires "all hands on desk" would better be done on your shell .

 

THE TERMINAL

This is just the common name for this type of application. For example, both Gnome Linux Environment and macOS call their application “Terminal”. But, the KDE linux Environment and Windows call it “Console”.

fields.title: Lord Of Scoundrel
fields.summary:
DETERMINED LADY

Tough-minded
Jessica Trent's sole intention is to free her nitwit brother from the
destructive influence of Sebastian Ballister, the notorious Marquess of
Dain. She never expects to desire the arrogant, amoral cad. And when Dain's reciprocal passion places them in a scandalously compromising, and public, position, Jessica is left with no choice but to seek satisfaction...

fields.title: Relative Betrayal
fields.summary: When Rachel's marriage had broken up there had been no possibility ofreconciliation. Not only had her husband, Matthew Conroy, looked elsewherefor love, but the woman he had chosen was Rachel's own cousin, Barbara

fields.title: legend of drizzt
fields.summary: Drizzt is back, and facing a world changed forever! An uneasy peace between the dwarves of Mithral Hall and the orcs of the newly established Kingdom of Many-Arrows can’t last long. The orc tribes united under Obould begin to fight each other, and Bruenor is determined to finish the war that nearly killed him and almost destroyed everything he’s worked to build. But it will take more than swords and axes to bring a lasting peace to the Spine of the World. Powerful individuals on both sides may have to change the way they see each other.
